            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary" style="">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            以点窥面看LCA          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">航空小筑的方方</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                方方的航空小筑              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">方方的航空小筑</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">ffaerofield</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">航迷自留地。非官宣消息都不知道。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true"></span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015136" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kRsNAVlvW6Ciby0Uf9uybK662IlSibY66e61KZsCCJyRZzrX8H5vYAENFg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="690" style=""></p><p>        LCA Mk1A于3月28日在班加罗尔完成首飞。对于这种飞机，也跟踪了10多年了，很多东西都推测过了。现在要做的就是验证。</p><p>        以下是起飞截图。按照这个估算，当前速度在280km/h左右，比起当初参考幻影2000估计的270km/h要大一点。考虑到此时并非离地速度，距离离地瞬间有2秒左右的加速时间，那么在视频条件下的起飞速度在270km/h左右应该是差不多的。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015138" data-ratio="0.7510683760683761" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kRZn0VqicicViaexiaO2SGta7d4dNShoL0PznXKcyaickVgP6CiaKNbqPc6rLw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="936" style=""></p><p>        考虑到该机只飞了18分钟就落地了，不可能加满油，为了让升力系数好看一些，取较大的起飞重量（半油，总重8000kg）。再结合班加罗尔的海拔（海高922米）和气温（正午33℃）对标准大气进行修正，反推LCA在视频中起飞时升力系数为0.52，这个就太低了(如果连半油都没加到的话，升力系数会更低），比幻影2000还要低得多，不过符合当年的预测和后面几次的粗略判断：</p><p>    《<a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNjY1MzAzMg==&amp;mid=2247483783&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7e7675c0ddb561e3f74ac754fb219f56&amp;chksm=9bf0ce00ac874716c3b7929b3b8ac54adc71de6640d644ea4c8b46c48734ab46e6b886bca206&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="LCA发展评述（原载《国际展望》）" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2">LCA发展评述</a>》</p><p><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015142" data-ratio="0.24259259259259258" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kRwPRx1naLT4r6ufp8dghNJt1eJExOcZpaVFJIaWMn4wOFOuA7xBmE0w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015143" data-ratio="0.4425925925925926" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kR4k8ZD87mqiaSSX2853yeITuCMGR4b9vaibpZMNJiaPzIiaStlXibIdztTew/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p>    《<a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNjY1MzAzMg==&amp;mid=2247495388&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a67019481dced1721f295458dd78ccd6&amp;chksm=9bf3215bac84a84ddfe0f56bdfd2718c35950fcfb5a2b72db602b03d739c81a36e2c38d91223&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="管窥LCA的升力特性" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2">管窥LCA的升力特性</a>》</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015140" data-ratio="0.45918367346938777" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kR0EBK5c8rws9SPhnTicbFoQNHXJDGqiajXeCW6d4Nal9hiatO19h0eYdjg/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="784" style=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100015141" data-ratio="0.17407407407407408" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH5zdEWU833KATndBhFvB6kRsqpovHeX3m29aW7VO8PD1HFtbmFto6O8AzQUiaWCQic0zw922pwb1lRg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p style="text-align: justify;">        所以这个Mk1A，从飞行性能上来说其实没什么改进之处。发动机推力略有增大，但个人判断是增强发电能力的附带结果。毕竟换了个相控阵雷达，供电能力是必须考虑的。</p><p style="text-align: justify;">        顺便表达一下对阿三宣传部门的钦佩之情。毕竟在他们笔下的LCA和实际的LCA，根本就是两种飞机。能够写成这个样子，不得不服。<br></p><p><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="713394768" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
